{
  "insurer": "liberty_videocon",
  "display_name": "Liberty General Insurance",
  "file_patterns": ["*Liberty*Robinhood*", "*Robinhood*Liberty*", "Robinhood*"],

  "_layout_notes": [
    "Liberty (Robinhood) ships one workbook per month with 6 motor sheets plus CL/Health (skipped — non-motor).",
    "Every motor sheet is a wide cross-tab: rows = state-cluster regions ('ANDHRA PRADESH - 1 KV'), columns = (segment × age/cc band × OD/SATP).",
    "The state-cluster string in column 0 is the join key against the RTO mapping file's 'Geo Cluster' sheet (3 cluster columns per RTO — one per product family).",
    "Age band labels in the source ('New', '>1 - 5', '>5 - 10', '>10') translate to {0-0, 1-5, 5-10, 10-99}.",
    "For weight bands, '<7.5T' / '12-20T' columns set weight_band_min/max in tonnes (matches HDFC/Chola/Shriram convention).",
    "TW bike CC bands: <75 / >75-150 / >150-350 / >350 → cc_band_min/max in CC.",
    "Pvt Car TP CC bands: <1000 / 1000-1500 / >1500 → cc_band_min/max in CC.",
    "RTO mapping is processed via the rto_mapping engine — three clusters per RTO are emitted as separate cluster_for_* fields in cluster column."
  ],

